Long-term storage for Home Assistant sensor data via DuckLake on Cloudflare R2.

## About

Samples a Group helper's entities every 30 minutes to flat per-entity monthly
CSV files, then nightly:

- consolidates new rows into a [DuckLake](https://ducklake.select/) (Parquet)
  on **Cloudflare R2**
- syncs raw CSVs to any `rclone` remote as a cold backup

Visualization on demand via `duckdb -ui` pointed at R2 — no dashboard server
to maintain.

